Class StandaloneTestCaseRun

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.centurylink.mdw.services.test.TestCaseRun
      • com.centurylink.mdw.services.test.StandaloneTestCaseRun
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class StandaloneTestCaseRun
extends TestCaseRun
    Executes a test outside of the runtime container. Used by Designer when debugging. Will eventually be used for all Designer runs. Will also be used by our upcoming Gradle custom task for test execution.
